About Senate Committee on Small Business and Entrepreneurship

About Senate Committee on Small Business and Entrepreneurship

The jurisdiction of the Senate Committee on Small Business and Entrepreneurship is specified in Rule XXV, Clause 1 of the Senate Manual. Visit the committee's website for more information including membership and rules.

The publications on this page are available at the committee's discretion. A "No results found" message below means there are currently no applicable publications in the system.
